{
  "name": "Tunneling Fang",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Inuzuka.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As part of the requirements of this jutsu you must have the Four Legs Technique active or your Nin-Dog must have Beast-Human Clone active. <br />You or your nin-dog begin to spin at an accelerated rate attempting a spiraling body slam. <br />Move up to 30 feet into an adjacent space next to the target creature and make a melee Taijutsu attack against it, so long as you can see or smell it within range. <br />On a hit, you deal 2d6 slashing and 2d6 bludgeoning damage. </p><p><br />At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and damage by 1d6 for each damage type.</p>",
